<h2>Loans that change lives.</h2>
<div class="showcase">
<p><strong>Micro-lending is a powerful tool for social progress.</strong> Keevahh is a non-profit organization with a mission to connect people through lending to alleviate poverty. Leveraging the internet and a worldwide network of microfinance institutions, Keevahh lets individuals lend as little as $25 to help create opportunity around the world.</p>
