</div>

<div class="showcase">
  <h2><%= link_to "Choose A Borrower", tenants_path %></h2>
  <p>Read through borrower stories of people looking for loans to grow businesses, go to school, switch to clean energy and more.</p>
  <p><strong>Find someone who connects with you.</strong> </p>
  <%= link_to(image_tag("arrowbutton.png", :alt => "Choose A Borrower"), tenants_path) %>
